They found his shirt, and then found the same shirt again. What was going on? They found his pants, and then found the same pants again. They followed a trail where they could trace him. They were looking for him in the woods. They found his wallet. All of its contents were still inside, including cash. They found his shoes. And then they found the same pair of shoes again. How strange.  Why would he leave behind two pairs of shoes? They kept looking. They found his hat. And then they found the same hat- again! They found his shirt, and then found the same shirt again. What was going on? They found his pants, and then found the same pants again. "Are you sure we're looking for the right guy?" said Ben Affleck. "I think we should stop looking for him and just wait for him to come back," said Ben Affleck. Just then, they heard a sound coming from behind a tree. It was Matt Damon! They ran over to him, when they heard a sound coming from behind another tree a few yards away

Just then, they heard a sound coming from behind a tree. It was Matt Damon! They ran over to him, when they heard a sound coming from behind another tree a few yards away.
